729537f-a.text:
Rockland Avenue, north side, 350 yards west of Forest Hill Woad, showing the Henry Meyer residence and part of his 49 acre estate (1907-1917 maps). The propemty was owned by E. C. Dissosway in 1898,
and by Jacob Korn in 1874.
May 9, 1926
P. L. Sperr
